 room and then treat symptoms with expensive and avoidable medical interven=
tions.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 2=
6px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">What does that look like in practice? Maybe the pe=
