itional healthcare waits until the fall, calls 911, and delivers thousands =
or tens of thousands of dollars worth of medical care. It&#8217;s a tragic =
game of whack-a-mole.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px;=
