children, pregnant women, and people with disabilities. Today,<strong> ther=
e are <a href=3D"https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkEmOgzAQRU8TL5GncszCi=
970NZCHglgBGxkTmtu3E9RqqVSjvr7qeVtxyuU0a94qeaehniuahMc2Y61YyL5hGWIwTHEtQPYk=
