lor: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">72.2 million Americans</a> on Me=
dicaid, including 50% of all babies born in the US and one out of every thr=
ee New Yorkers</strong>.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16=
px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">In 2019, state and federal gover=
nments spent <strong>$613.5 billion</strong> on Medicaid, and according to =
a <a href=3D"https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFUcGOhCAM_ZrhpgEU1AOHvexvG=
