ITWRrCW7HPbSv9D_wHwwJxo" style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underlin=
e;">Silicon Valley is too focused on taking the easy path in healthcare</a>=
,&#8221; Christina Farr wrote:&nbsp;</p><blockquote style=3D"border-left: 4=
